Date: Sun, 26 Oct 2025 20:03:26 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 05/64] mediatek: filogic: refine dts files to support hnat and
 mtwifi - for mt7981, since it hasnt been included in upstream yet, we do
 modification to it directly - for mt7986, we add patches to do the same work

Signed-off-by: chasey-dev <ellenyoung0912@gmail.com>
---
 .../arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7981.dtsi  |  88 +++++---
 ...hnat-add-mtkhnat-support-for-mt7986a.patch |  23 ++
 ...t7986a-ethsys-from-mtk-openwrt-feeds.patch |  39 ++++
